{{Refimprove|date=April 2010}} {{Primary sources|date=April 2010}} [[File:PreciousHeartRomancesLogo.jpg|right]]'''Precious Hearts Romances Presents''' is an ABS-CBN program mainly focusing on adaptations of the best-selling pocketbooks distributed by company holder, ''Precious Hearts Romances''.
